test.doc: We would like to know whether an authenticated user can add an item to their wishlist and then delete it. For this we need a registered user on the website. We also will verify that the wishlist counter shows exactly 1. Once we're done with the scenario, we will log out in order to decouple the test from other possible tests and from future runs of the same test.
